  "explanation": "The defendant is a first-time offender who committed a non-violent financial crime. While embezzlement is a serious breach of trust, the amount of $25,000 is relatively modest and partial restitution has been made. External outbursts by courtroom spectators are irrelevant to the sentencing calculation. Taking into account the defendant's lack of a prior record and the specific circumstances of the theft, a short period of incarceration serves as sufficient deterrence and punishment.",
